ism in the pre-Triassic basement of\nthe Northern Apennines. The potential relationships between Permian felsic\nmagmatism and the ore genesis in the Alpi Apuane metamorphic complex are also\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Dec 2018 11:10:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-27"}
